[SPEAKER_00] proročka kontemplacija,

516
00:33:28,140 --> 00:33:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] proročki način služenja.

517
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] sve ono što mi

518
00:33:33,619 --> 00:33:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] želimo služiti,

519
00:33:35,900 --> 00:33:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] raditi,

520
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,299
[SPEAKER_00] djelovati,

521
00:33:37,299 --> 00:33:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] bi trebalo iz ove,

522
00:33:38,539 --> 00:33:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] iz ovog P,

523
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] pokreniti se.

524
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bit u njegove prisutnosti

525
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] i gledati ono što ti Bog daje.

526
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:49,660
[SPEAKER_00] Šut ono što Bog govori.

527
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kad gledaš proroke,

528
00:33:51,559 --> 00:33:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] pojedinačno,

529
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] i dođe riječ Božja,

530
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] prorok u tome.

531
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, riječ dođe,

532
00:33:59,380 --> 00:33:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] ima noge,

533
00:33:59,900 --> 00:34:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] dođe.

534
00:34:02,859 --> 00:34:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] ili kad ono,

535
00:34:04,259 --> 00:34:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] gleda,

536
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] gleda,

537
00:34:05,539 --> 00:34:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] ono proroč,

538
00:34:06,359 --> 00:34:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] dođe,

539
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] što vidiš proroče?

540
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što gledaš?

541
00:34:11,980 --> 00:34:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] I onda on kaže,

542
00:34:12,739 --> 00:34:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gledam,

543
00:34:13,579 --> 00:34:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

544
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] stablo,

545
00:34:15,539 --> 00:34:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

546
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] dobro,

547
00:34:17,079 --> 00:34:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] i onda još malo,

548
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] molitva,

549
00:34:19,019 --> 00:34:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] pa što sad vidiš?

550
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] da vidim to,

551
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] to,

552
00:34:21,539 --> 00:34:21,840
[SPEAKER_00] to.

553
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo nekako slika Ezekijela,

554
00:34:26,420 --> 00:34:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] suhe kosti.

555
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan poticaj,

556
00:34:30,239 --> 00:34:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] meni odavno,

557
00:34:31,039 --> 00:34:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] vezano za proročku dimenziju.

558
00:34:33,300 --> 00:34:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

559
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] prvo,

560
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] duh go progovara proroku i suhim kostima.

561
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pita ga,

562
00:34:42,059 --> 00:34:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] je li ja mogu živjeti ove kosti?

563
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] Je li ja mogu,

564
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

565
00:34:45,260 --> 00:34:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] ti najbolje znaš?

566
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

567
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] prorokuj mojim kostima.

568
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

569
00:34:49,719 --> 00:34:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] prorok,

570
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] dobio je riječ koju treba izgovarati kostima

571
00:34:53,659 --> 00:34:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] i prorokuje kostima.

572
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] I kosti se počinju micati,

573
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] povezivati,

574
00:34:58,820 --> 00:34:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] meso,

575
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] tkivo,

576
00:35:00,019 --> 00:35:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

577
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:01,719
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kaže,

578
00:35:01,719 --> 00:35:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

579
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] vidje da nije dovoljno

580
00:35:05,179 --> 00:35:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

581
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] proroče prorokuj duhu.

582
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] I onda on počinje prorokovat riječi koju mu je dao

583
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,699
[SPEAKER_00] i to se,

584
00:35:15,699 --> 00:35:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

585
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju povezalo sve u zajedništvu

586
00:35:19,579 --> 00:35:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] i bi velika vojska Božja.

587
00:35:21,659 --> 00:35:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dvije dimenzije,

588
00:35:24,139 --> 00:35:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] proročke dimenzije,

589
00:35:26,559 --> 00:35:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] proroštvo na razini tijela

590
00:35:29,679 --> 00:35:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] i proroštvo na razini duha.

591
00:35:32,739 --> 00:35:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] Proroštvo na razini tijela je kada dobijemo poticaj,

592
00:35:38,559 --> 00:35:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] proroštvo riječ Božju,

593
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] koja se tiče našeg života,

594
00:35:42,699 --> 00:35:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] utjeha opomena,

595
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] što god treba,

596
00:35:47,500 --> 00:35:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] zadovoljenje nekih želja naših.

597
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,800
[SPEAKER_00] Bog hoće progovarati.

598
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] A prorokovanje duhu je veća dimenzija

599
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] da se mi otvaramo njegovoj prisutnosti

600
00:35:59,519 --> 00:36:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] i čujemo i imamo uvide u ono što dolazi poslje.

601
00:36:05,059 --> 00:36:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta ste ovako kad smo bili na zajednicu,

602
00:36:10,500 --> 00:36:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] čuli riječ koja nas tamo u budućnost vodi.

603
00:36:14,559 --> 00:36:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] I ta riječ vidimo po nekim etapama se ostvaruje

604
00:36:18,139 --> 00:36:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođe punina vremena.

605
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ta proročka kontemplacija,

606
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] proročko gledanje,

607
00:36:24,219 --> 00:36:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] otkriva Božje namisli za ovo vrijeme

608
00:36:28,739 --> 00:36:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] i za ono što nas čeka.

609
00:36:30,559 --> 00:36:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, Bog ne ostavlja svoje

610
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] bez da im objavi što će se dogoditi.

611
00:36:36,159 --> 00:36:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Samo nema nas u tom odnosu

612
00:36:39,599 --> 00:36:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mogli čut to što nam On želi objasniti.

613
00:36:43,940 --> 00:36:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] I kad ti progovori duhu,

614
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] ti se treseš od miline.

615
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se treseš od te ljubavi, riječi

616
00:36:51,739 --> 00:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] koja stvara u tebi novi život,

617
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] novu sliku, novu viziju, novo sve.

618
00:36:57,159 --> 00:36:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je uvijek novi.

619
00:36:59,139 --> 00:37:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] Danas što si primio, sutra možda ne vrijedi.

620
00:37:03,079 --> 00:37:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne živimo na staroj slavi,

621
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] nego svaki dan je novi.

622
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] Novi početak, novi izljev duha svetoga,

623
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] novo otkrivenje duha svetoga

624
00:37:12,519 --> 00:37:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] zato što ti želi dati novu hranu.

625
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] I mi nekad uzmemo proroštva koja su bila

626
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] od prije tri, četiri, pet godina

627
00:37:21,599 --> 00:37:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to živimo.

628
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] I ne želimo otvarati novu dimenziju.

629
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog nama govori

630
00:37:27,739 --> 00:37:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj se zadržavati na osvojenim spoznajama.

631
00:37:33,659 --> 00:37:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] To znači da ti je Bog dao spoznaju,

632
00:37:36,559 --> 00:37:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] došao si do nekog nivoa

633
00:37:38,179 --> 00:37:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] i tu si stao.

634
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je dao tu spoznaju.

635
00:37:41,519 --> 00:37:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog ti želi dati novu spoznaju,

636
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] veću spoznaju.

637
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ako smo mi otvoreni,

638
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj osvajati ono u duhovnom svijetu.

639
00:37:49,119 --> 00:37:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Došao si do nekog.

640
00:37:50,219 --> 00:37:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] E, to je dosta.

641
00:37:51,519 --> 00:37:53,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja kažem da je dosta,

642
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,719
[SPEAKER_00] ja počinjem padat.

643
00:37:54,719 --> 00:37:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što Bog želi dati više.

644
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što Bog progovara,

645
00:38:02,039 --> 00:38:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, ovako bi ja to rekao,

646
00:38:05,199 --> 00:38:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] bez vizije pogleda njegovoga,

647
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su duhovno mrtvi.

648
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako nemam proročki uvid

649
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] u svoj život, u život zajednice,

650
00:38:19,059 --> 00:38:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] u život kakvode sa crkve,

651
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] mi duhovno umiremo.

652
00:38:22,980 --> 00:38:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže na jednom mjestu u psalmu,

653
00:38:25,539 --> 00:38:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

654
00:38:27,119 --> 00:38:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi Bog ne progovori,

655
00:38:29,559 --> 00:38:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] ja umirem.

656
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Slobodan tumačenje.

657
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako mi On ne progovori,

658
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja umirem.

659
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo pozvani doći pred lice njegovo,

660
00:38:38,619 --> 00:38:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] da nam On progovara svoje riječi.

661
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] I što više dolazimo,

662
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] više prepoznajemo njegov glas.

663
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bog čini nove stvari u meni,

664
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] u tebi, u životu,

665
00:38:49,900 --> 00:38:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] u životu zajednice.

666
00:38:51,039 --> 00:38:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bog želi tebe voditi tamo,

667
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,820
[SPEAKER_00] gdje još nisi bio.

668
00:38:57,119 --> 00:39:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] A mi nekad u našim okvirima,

669
00:39:00,679 --> 00:39:04,760
[SPEAKER_00] možda zarobljenosti želimo poboljšati uvjete.

670
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, živimo u tom ropstvu,

671
00:39:07,719 --> 00:39:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] u tom zatvoru,

672
00:39:08,559 --> 00:39:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] e onda ću kupiti novi TV,

673
00:39:10,559 --> 00:39:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] novi laptop,

674
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] da mi bude bolje,

675
00:39:14,059 --> 00:39:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] da mi bude ljepše.

676
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog kaže, ne, ja te želim voditi tamo,

677
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] gdje nisi do sada bio.

678
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što meni,

679
00:39:20,559 --> 00:39:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] meni je ono,

680
00:39:21,659 --> 00:39:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao,

681
00:39:23,159 --> 00:39:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] slika koja mi je došla,

682
00:39:25,619 --> 00:39:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom trenutku,

683
00:39:27,059 --> 00:39:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] vrata zatvorena.

684
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, imamo vrata zatvorena,

685
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] znači zatvorena vrata

686
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] i u jednom trenutku će Bog otvoriti ta vrata.

687
00:39:38,019 --> 00:39:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pitanje je za sve nas,

688
00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] sam li ja spreman kad Bog otvori vrata,

689
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] proći kroz ta vrata?

690
00:39:44,619 --> 00:39:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ili nisam?

691
00:39:46,119 --> 00:39:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li spreman za to?

692
00:39:50,059 --> 00:39:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kad gledamo dar jezika,

693
00:39:54,039 --> 00:40:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači dar jezika te uvodi u kontemplaciju

694
00:40:00,179 --> 00:40:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] i to proročko gledanje.

695
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] Samo treba moliti.

696
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sam zapisao ovdje,

697
00:40:06,599 --> 00:40:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] taj dar jezika,

698
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] bila jedna anketa po našim zajednicama

699
00:40:11,079 --> 00:40:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] i svaki u anonimnosti treba odgovoriti na dva pitanja.

700
00:40:15,139 --> 00:40:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko moliš daru jezika dnevno, tjedno,

701
00:40:20,059 --> 00:40:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] od suseda do suseta mjesečno.

702
00:40:22,599 --> 00:40:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] I kad se napravi cijeli prosjek,

703
00:40:25,559 --> 00:40:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo karizmatska obnova,

704
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] to su zajednice u Zagrebu,

705
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] parnih zajednica koje su imale u anketu,

706
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] prosjek ispada pet minuta.

707
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi, mi odrađujemo pet minuta,

708
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] halalalalalala.

709
00:40:39,340 --> 00:40:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] To znači da mogu moliti dva sata na zajednici,

710
00:40:42,659 --> 00:40:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] halalalala, Marija, halala i šest dana ništa.

711
00:40:45,639 --> 00:40:47,179
[SPEAKER_00] Pet minuta.

712
00:40:47,179 --> 00:40:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] A kaže osobna molitva,

713
00:40:50,059 --> 00:40:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] znači prebivati u Božoj prisutnosti,

714
00:40:53,599 --> 00:40:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] anketa je pokazala petnes minuta.

715
00:40:56,179 --> 00:40:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moji, petnes minuta.

716
00:40:58,579 --> 00:41:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] A kaže, izvoj sat vremena.

717
00:41:01,099 --> 00:41:02,760
[SPEAKER_00] A mi petnest u prosjeku.

718
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] Neko ono ima tri, četiri sata,

719
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] a neko nema ništa.

720
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nakraju ispadne petnes minuta.

721
00:41:07,679 --> 00:41:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] Za petnes minuta ti ne možeš ništa primati

722
00:41:11,679 --> 00:41:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] ni ti gledati u njegovom duhu.

723
00:41:16,639 --> 00:41:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ako treba, Bog će ti dati.

724
00:41:18,179 --> 00:41:22,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to nije životni stil koji treba, voditelj, živjeti.

725
00:41:22,139 --> 00:41:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] To nije životni stil koji treba njegovati.

726
00:41:28,599 --> 00:41:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta u molitvi ne znamo što treba moliti.

727
00:41:31,139 --> 00:41:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta ne znamo što treba moliti.

728
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gospodin, kada dođeš u njegovu prisutnost,

729
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] čuje tvoje srce.

730
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čuje srce kako ti kuca.

731
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] Čuje srce kako ti govori.

732
00:41:44,719 --> 00:41:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] Čuje srce kako on čuje tvoje srce kako funkcionira.

733
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] I on nas uvodi u tu dimenziju da nas i trenira,

734
00:41:55,739 --> 00:41:59,320
[SPEAKER_00] da nas obučava, da nas mijenja, da nas ozdravlja,

735
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] da nas oslobađa.

736
00:42:01,059 --> 00:42:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] On nas trenira u tom proročkom promatranju

737
00:42:04,820 --> 00:42:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili osluškivanju što nam Bog treba dati.

738
00:42:07,159 --> 00:42:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jesmo li mi spremni svaki dan vježbati?

739
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja svaki dan, danas, pa za godinu dana,

740
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] dolazim u njegovu prisutnost

741
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] i on mi progovara sigurno da će me pripremiti

742
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] za sve duhovne borbe, za sve duhovne situacije,

743
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] da se pobjede sile zla,

744
00:42:22,739 --> 00:42:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] da se pobjede sve ono što imamo u životu.

745
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako ja ne treniram, kada dođe ta situacija,

746
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:32,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači kada ulaziš u duhovnu borbu,

747
00:42:32,179 --> 00:42:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] ti imaš problem, jer nisi treniran,

748
00:42:34,179 --> 00:42:39,179
[SPEAKER_00] a trenira se jedan na jedan sa gospodinom.

749
00:42:39,179 --> 00:42:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Upoznaješ njegovo srce, upoznaješ što je on,

750
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:44,639
[SPEAKER_00] upoznaješ šta i kako živi,

751
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:47,239
[SPEAKER_00] i ti postaješ izvor njegovo.

752
00:42:47,239 --> 00:42:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ti postaješ izvor svetosti,

753
00:42:49,699 --> 00:42:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] ti postaješ izvor čistoće,

754
00:42:52,119 --> 00:42:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] ti postaješ izvor gdje on,

755
00:42:54,619 --> 00:42:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] znači to iskustvo koje susreta,

756
00:42:57,320 --> 00:43:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] tebe preobražava i mijenja

757
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] da bi moglo biti svjetlo tamo gdje te šalje.

758
00:43:03,460 --> 00:43:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zadnje slovo, evangelizacija.

759
00:43:06,820 --> 00:43:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] Neću govoriti o metodama evangelizacije,

760
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] nije ni bila namjera,

761
00:43:11,639 --> 00:43:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] nego stav, znači sve ove pokajanje,

762
00:43:15,119 --> 00:43:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] oduševljenje,

763
00:43:16,039 --> 00:43:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] proročko, promatranje,

764
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] dovodite u akciju,

765
00:43:20,940 --> 00:43:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] u evangelizaciju.

766
00:43:22,440 --> 00:43:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što prva riječ,

767
00:43:25,019 --> 00:43:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] kada sam stao nad evangelizacijom,

768
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] evangelizacijom,

769
00:43:28,239 --> 00:43:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] bila je rečenica za ovaj susret,

770
00:43:31,019 --> 00:43:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] meni upućena,

771
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da se možete svi u ovom svjedočanstvu prepoznat,

772
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,219
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

773
00:43:36,219 --> 00:43:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] idi tamo gdje ne osjećaš da trebaš ići.

774
00:43:40,079 --> 00:43:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, idi tamo gdje ne osjećaš da trebaš ići.

775
00:43:47,420 --> 00:43:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] Izlike mi radimo,

776
00:43:49,420 --> 00:43:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] a ja ne osjećam da treba ići tamo.

777
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne osjećam da treba ići susjedu koji je u problemima,

778
00:43:57,039 --> 00:44:01,179
[SPEAKER_00] jer on neće shvatiti ako mu ja dođem.

779
00:44:01,179 --> 00:44:04,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ili, kad gledam ono,

780
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] ne sviđa mi se to,

781
00:44:05,699 --> 00:44:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa neću ja to raditi.

782
00:44:08,099 --> 00:44:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moji,

783
00:44:08,739 --> 00:44:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] Isus Krist je išao u Jeruzalem,

784
00:44:11,780 --> 00:44:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] znajući da će ga razapeti.

785
00:44:16,159 --> 00:44:18,659
[SPEAKER_00] A mogo je koristiti osjećaj,

786
00:44:18,659 --> 00:44:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] aha, oni će me tamo razapeta,

787
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] neću ja tamo iću.

788
00:44:21,559 --> 00:44:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, ne sviđa mi se to,

789
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] ni malo da će me razapeta.

790
00:44:24,840 --> 00:44:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] Joj.

791
00:44:26,199 --> 00:44:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] Introvert, da.

792
00:44:30,460 --> 00:44:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ili ono,

793
00:44:33,199 --> 00:44:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] idi siromasima,

794
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] papa govori svima nama,

795
00:44:36,579 --> 00:44:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] idite siromasima,

796
00:44:38,099 --> 00:44:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] i donesite im ono što imate.

797
00:44:40,300 --> 00:44:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] Prva reakcija,

798
00:44:42,119 --> 00:44:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] kada ti se sjetiš da bi trebao

799
00:44:44,059 --> 00:44:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] ići siromasima,

800
00:44:45,340 --> 00:44:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] donijeti krštenje u duhu,

801
00:44:48,400 --> 00:44:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili bilo što,

802
00:44:49,159 --> 00:44:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] joj, ne da mi se.

803
00:44:50,619 --> 00:44:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sigurno Bog mene ne zove na to.

804
00:44:53,239 --> 00:44:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Možda zove ove malo otkačenije,

805
00:44:55,659 --> 00:44:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] ove na novo rođene

806
00:44:56,760 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] i Božju pobjedu i sl.

807
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mene tamo sa siromašnjima

808
00:45:01,039 --> 00:45:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] ne zove, ne da mi se.

809
00:45:02,800 --> 00:45:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Bog poziva da idemo onima

810
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] koje nitko neće.

811
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] I kada ja imam taj stav

812
00:45:11,559 --> 00:45:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] da idem bratu i sestri u potrebi,

813
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] događaju se čudesa.

814
00:45:16,139 --> 00:45:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da ste vi

815
00:45:18,519 --> 00:45:20,219
[SPEAKER_00] toko puto upotrebljeni

816
00:45:20,219 --> 00:45:22,159
[SPEAKER_00] da vas je Bog poslao

817
00:45:22,159 --> 00:45:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji nitko neće.

818
00:45:23,659 --> 00:45:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su zaglibili u grijehu,

819
00:45:26,300 --> 00:45:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] u svom životnom stanju,

820
00:45:27,880 --> 00:45:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] staležu.

821
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bog po vama donosi pobjedu

822
00:45:31,539 --> 00:45:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] u njihove živote

823
00:45:32,579 --> 00:45:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] događaju se obraćenja

824
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] mnoga svjedočanstva.

825
00:45:35,719 --> 00:45:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

826
00:45:37,639 --> 00:45:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što se na vama,

827
00:45:38,900 --> 00:45:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] na nama vidi

828
00:45:40,199 --> 00:45:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bog koji je živ.

829
00:45:42,380 --> 00:45:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si pozvana.

830
00:45:44,280 --> 00:45:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pozvana.

831
00:45:45,860 --> 00:45:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pozdraviti crku koja je u problemima.

832
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si pozvana.

833
00:45:51,199 --> 00:45:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je puna svega.

834
00:45:53,639 --> 00:45:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je Božje dijelo,

835
00:45:58,619 --> 00:45:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kristovo dijelo.

836
00:46:00,320 --> 00:46:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] i pokut Krista,

837
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] ona daje svoj život

838
00:46:03,460 --> 00:46:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] za Boga.

839
00:46:05,840 --> 00:46:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva, to si ti.

840
00:46:08,719 --> 00:46:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] To sam ja,

841
00:46:10,179 --> 00:46:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je svak od nas.

842
00:46:11,059 --> 00:46:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mi bi trebali dati svoj život

843
00:46:13,199 --> 00:46:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] za Boga.

844
00:46:14,260 --> 00:46:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljajte mlade živote.

845
00:46:17,760 --> 00:46:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljajte brakove.

846
00:46:20,860 --> 00:46:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljajte i oslobađajte obitelji

847
00:46:24,579 --> 00:46:25,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji su u ropstvima.

848
00:46:25,719 --> 00:46:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] I budimo prisutni za one

849
00:46:29,579 --> 00:46:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji su u potrebi.

850
00:46:31,840 --> 00:46:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

